🚀 Idea Vault Server
This is the backend server for the "Idea Vault" full-stack web application. It handles core functionalities including idea management, user activity tracking, a comment system, and booking services.

🛠 Tech Stack
Runtime: Node.js

Framework: Express.js

Database: MongoDB (using native driver)

Authentication: JWT (Better Auth support)

Deployment: Vercel

📋 API Endpoints
💡 Idea Routes
POST /api/idea - Create a new idea (Protected)

GET /api/idea - Fetch all ideas (with search & category filters)

GET /api/idea/:id - Fetch a specific idea

PATCH /api/idea/:id - Update an idea

DELETE /api/idea/:id - Delete an idea

🏃 Activity Routes
GET /api/activity - View user activity logs (Protected)

DELETE /api/activity/:id - Delete an activity log (Protected)

💬 Comment Routes
GET /api/comments - Fetch all comments

POST /api/comments - Create a new comment (Protected)

PATCH /api/comments/:id - Update a comment (Protected)

DELETE /api/comments/:id - Delete a comment (Protected)

🎫 Booking Routes
GET /api/bookings - Fetch all bookings

POST /api/bookings - Create a new booking

⚙️ Local Setup
Clone the repository.

Create a .env file and add the following variables:

Code snippet
BETTER_AUTH_SECRECT
MONGO_DB_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000
PORT=5000

## 🚀 Deployment

To deploy your project to production using Vercel CLI:

```bash
vercel --prod
Note: This project currently runs as a single-file implementation (server.js). For better scalability and maintainability, refactoring the code into separate controllers and routes is recommended for future updates.
```
